data.description: Don't Miss Out on Low Interest Rates! Your Opportunity to Benefit Awaits!  Take advantage of this incredible offer for qualified buyers - a 2.75% assumable mortgage on a stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bath custom-built manufactured home. With its open floor plan and a spacious kitchen featuring a large island, this residence is perfect for hosting gatherings with family and friends.  The master bedroom boasts a luxurious en-suite with a generous walk-in closet, a soothing soaker tub, and an elegant walk-in shower. Each bedroom comes with its own walk-in closet, providing ample storage space for all your needs.  Nestled on 1.978 acres of beautifully cleared land, this property offers a serene and private setting and located within 5 minutes of Lake D'Arbonne. Don't let this opportunity pass you by to own a dream home at an attractive interest rate. Act now and make this your forever home!
